question: Do you perceive yourself in part for what people think of you more than you have a strong self identity that doesn't depend on anyone else? In other words, would your self identity change if you were invisible to others?
Do you tend to want to leave things unfinished if you are not careful more than finishing them before starting something new?
Would it be really hard for you not to cry and get emotional a lot if you see a dog really in pain crying in front of you and you can't help?
Do you often get distracted in your own thoughts more than living in the physical present life even when you are outside socializing?
